<def f='qtbase-6.5.0/src/3rdparty/harfbuzz-ng/src/hb-buffer.cc' l='1763' ll='1771' type='void hb_buffer_add_utf8(hb_buffer_t * buffer, const char * text, int text_length, unsigned int item_offset, int item_length)'/>
<doc f='qtbase-6.5.0/src/3rdparty/harfbuzz-ng/src/hb-buffer.cc' l='1746'>/**
 * hb_buffer_add_utf8:
 * @buffer: An #hb_buffer_t
 * @text: (array length=text_length) (element-type uint8_t): An array of UTF-8
 *               characters to append.
 * @text_length: The length of the @text, or -1 if it is `NULL` terminated.
 * @item_offset: The offset of the first character to add to the @buffer.
 * @item_length: The number of characters to add to the @buffer, or -1 for the
 *               end of @text (assuming it is `NULL` terminated).
 *
 * See hb_buffer_add_codepoints().
 *
 * Replaces invalid UTF-8 characters with the @buffer replacement code point,
 * see hb_buffer_set_replacement_codepoint().
 *
 * Since: 0.9.2
 **/</doc>
